        block based editing supports rich text formatiing like markdown pages 
        this allows each block to be its own separate component offering various types like image text and text types like bold itallic or everything that is supported by markdown 
        along with which supports features like link to external nodes of blocks  
        blocks can be text notes ,calender events,images link to other files,and code or anything else
    </description>

    <feature>
         Databases with Multiple Views
    </feature>
    <description>
        the blocks can store rich variety of data objects like calenders tables kanban boards timeline list schedulers and knowledge graph
        each block can have nested blocks as and each block may be link to one another 
    </description>

    <feature>
        Templates along with Drag-and-Drop Layouts
    </feature>
    <description>
        the blocks are also builtin for templtes for specifific use cases like students deveopers reserchers project managers
